{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775832706869,"sessionID":"ses_2882059dfffe6muPqJaYrql7KT","part":{"id":"prt_d77e0af310010R5IYPgE6mic1y","messageID":"msg_d77e0aa49001ISIc1QXznrBNnx","sessionID":"ses_2882059dfffe6muPqJaYrql7KT","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775832708357,"sessionID":"ses_2882059dfffe6muPqJaYrql7KT","part":{"id":"prt_d77e0b163001U6PoWmOt1ZYpji","messageID":"msg_d77e0aa49001ISIc1QXznrBNnx","sessionID":"ses_2882059dfffe6muPqJaYrql7KT","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_5b4f5e2674304329bad11f42","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-009: Router HTTP 反向代理核心 — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: 为 agentcube 项目新建 `pkg/router` 模块，实现基于 Go 的 HTTP 反向代理核心，作为系统的流量入口。该模块负责：(1) 通过 session ID 解析或创建 sandbox，(2) 将 HTTP 请求反向代理到 sandbox pod 的 entry point，(3) 为 sandbox 请求注入 RS256 JWT 签名，(4) 通过 client-go Informer 监听 CRD 变更实现动态服务发现，(5) 提供负载均衡、健康检查、并发限制中间件。本变更是对 AR-003（CRD 类型定义）、AR-005（Sandbox 创建）、AR-007（Reconciler）的下游消费方，同时解锁 AR-010+ 的高级流量治理能力。\n6: \n7: ## Requirements\n8: \n9: ### Requirement: Config 结构体与 CLI 标志\n10: \n11: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/config.go` 中定义 `Config` 结构体，包含以下字段：\n12: - `Port string` — 监听端口，默认 `\"8080\"`\n13: - `Debug bool` — 是否启用 Gin debug 模式，默认 `false`\n14: - `EnableTLS bool` — 是否启用 TLS，默认 `false`\n15: - `TLSCert string` — TLS 证书路径\n16: - `TLSKey string` — TLS 私钥路径\n17: - `MaxConcurrentRequests int` — 最大并发请求数，默认 `1000`（≤0 时 NewServer 内部设为 1000）\n18: \n19: `cmd/router/main.go` SHALL 解析以下 CLI 标志并构造 `Config`：\n20: \n21: | Flag | 类型 | 默认值 |\n22: |------|------|--------|\n23: | `-port` | string | `\"8080\"` |\n24: | `-debug` | bool | `false` |\n25: | `-enable-tls` | bool | `false` |\n26: | `-tls-cert` | string | `\"\"` |\n27: | `-tls-key` | string | `\"\"` |\n28: | `-max-concurrent-requests` | int | `1000` |\n29: \n30: #### Scenario: 默认配置\n31: \n32: - **GIVEN** 未传入任何 CLI 标志\n33: - **WHEN** `main()` 解析标志\n34: - **THEN** `Config.Port = \"8080\"`，`Config.Debug = false`，`Config.EnableTLS = false`，`Config.MaxConcurrentRequests = 1000`\n35: \n36: #### Scenario: MaxConcurrentRequests 为 0 时 NewServer 设为 1000\n37: \n38: - **GIVEN** `Config.MaxConcurrentRequests = 0`\n39: - **WHEN** `NewServer(config)` 被调用\n40: - **THEN** `config.MaxConcurrentRequests` 被设为 `1000`\n41: \n42: #### Scenario: 自定义配置覆盖默认值\n43: \n44: - **GIVEN** CLI 标志 `-port=9090 -debug -max-concurrent-requests=500`\n45: - **WHEN** `main()` 解析标志\n46: - **THEN** `Config.Port = \"9090\"`，`Config.Debug = true`，`Config.MaxConcurrentRequests = 500`\n47: \n48: ---\n49: \n50: ### Requirement: Server 结构体与构造函数\n51: \n52: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/server.go` 中定义 `Server` 结构体，包含以下字段：\n53: - `config *Config` — 配置\n54: - `engine *gin.Engine` — Gin 路由引擎\n55: - `httpServer *http.Server` — 标准库 HTTP 服务器\n56: - `sessionManager SessionManager` — 会话管理器接口\n57: - `storeClient store.Store` — Store 客户端\n58: - `httpTransport *http.Transport` — 共享 HTTP 传输层\n59: - `jwtManager *JWTManager` — JWT 管理器\n60: \n61: `httpTransport` SHALL 配置为：`IdleConnTimeout: 0`（不回收空闲连接），`DisableCompression: false`（启用压缩）。\n62: \n63: `NewServer(config *Config) (*Server, error)` SHALL：\n64: 1. 若 `config.MaxConcurrentRequests <= 0`，设为 `1000`\n65: 2. 构造 `httpTransport`\n66: 3. 初始化 Gin engine（`DebugMode` 若 `config.Debug`，否则 `ReleaseMode`）\n67: 4. 构造 `JWTManager` 并调用 `TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret`，失败则返回错误（in-cluster 跳过路径除外）\n68: 5. 构造 `SessionManager`（读取 `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` 环境变量）\n69: 6. 构造 `store.Store` 实例\n70: 7. 注册路由\n71: 8. 构造 `httpServer`\n72: \n73: #### Scenario: Debug 模式设置\n74: \n75: - **GIVEN** `config.Debug = true`\n76: - **WHEN** `NewServer(config)` 被调用\n77: - **THEN** `gin.SetMode(gin.DebugMode)`\n78: \n79: #### Scenario: Release 模式设置\n80: \n81: - **GIVEN** `config.Debug = false`\n82: - **WHEN** `NewServer(config)` 被调用\n83: - **THEN** `gin.SetMode(gin.ReleaseMode)`\n84: \n85: #### Scenario: JWT 密钥初始化失败导致 Server 创建失败\n86: \n87: - **GIVEN** `TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret` 返回非 nil 错误且非 in-cluster skip 路径\n88: - **WHEN** `NewServer(config)` 被调用\n89: - **THEN** 返回错误，Server 不为 nil 的条件不满足\n90: \n91: #### Scenario: WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL 未设置导致 Server 创建失败\n92: \n93: - **GIVEN** 环境变量 `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` 未设置\n94: - **WHEN** `NewServer(config)` 构造 SessionManager\n95: - **THEN** 返回错误 `\"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL environment variable is not set\"`\n96: \n97: ---\n98: \n99: ### Requirement: SessionManager 接口\n100: \n101: The system SHALL 定义 `SessionManager` 接口：\n102: \n103: ```go\n104: type SessionManager interface {\n105:     GetSandboxBySession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, namespace string, name string, kind string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n106: }\n107: ```\n108: \n109: #### Scenario: 接口方法签名\n110: \n111: - **GIVEN** `SessionManager` 接口定义\n112: - **WHEN** 编译 `pkg/router`\n113: - **THEN** 接口包含 `GetSandboxBySession` 方法，签名如上\n114: \n115: ---\n116: \n117: ### Requirement: Session Manager 实现\n118: \n119: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/session_manager.go` 中实现 `SessionManager` 接口：\n120: \n121: `manager` 结构体包含：\n122: - `storeClient store.Store`\n123: - `workloadMgrAddr string`\n124: - `httpClient *http.Client`\n125: \n126: `NewSessionManager(storeClient store.Store) (SessionManager, error)` SHALL：\n127: 1. 读取环境变量 `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL`，为空则返回错误 `\"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL environment variable is not set\"`\n128: 2. 构造 `http.Client`：`Timeout: 2 * time.Minute`\n129: 3. 构造 `http.Transport`：`MaxIdleConnsPerHost: 100`，`DisableCompression: false`\n130: 4. 调用 `http2.ConfigureTransports` 配置 `ReadIdleTimeout: 30s`，`PingTimeout: 15s`\n131: \n132: `GetSandboxBySession` SHALL：\n133: 1. 若 `sessionID` 非空，调用 `storeClient.GetSandbox(ctx, sessionID)` 获取 `SandboxInfo`\n134: 2. 若 Store 返回 `ErrNotFound`，返回 `NewSessionNotFoundError(sessionID)`\n135: 3. 若 `sessionID` 为空，POST 到 WorkloadManager 创建 sandbox\n136: 4. 创建请求的 URL：`AgentRuntime` → `{addr}/v1/agent-runtime`，`CodeInterpreter` → `{addr}/v1/code-interpreter`\n137: 5. 请求体：JSON `{\"kind\":\"<kind>\",\"name\":\"<name>\",\"namespace\":\"<namespace>\"}`\n138: 6. 若 `/var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/token` 存在且可读，附加 `Authorization: Bearer <trimmed contents>`\n139: 7. 响应 200 时解析 `CreateSandboxResponse`，构建 `SandboxInfo`\n140: 8. 响应非 200 时返回 `NewSandboxTemplateNotFoundError(namespace, name, kind)`\n141: 9. 若响应体 `sessionId` 为空，返回内部错误\n142: \n143: #### Scenario: 缺失 WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL 导致构造失败\n144: \n145: - **GIVEN** `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` 未设置\n146: - **WHEN** `NewSessionManager(storeClient)` 被调用\n147: - **THEN** 返回错误 `\"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL environment variable is not set\"`\n148: \n149: #### Scenario: 已知 sessionID 从 Store 获取 SandboxInfo\n150: \n151: - **GIVEN** Store 中存在 `sess-001` 条目\n152: - **WHEN** `GetSandboxBySession(ctx, \"sess-001\", \"default\", \"my-runtime\", \"AgentRuntime\")` 被调用\n153: - **THEN** 返回对应的 `*types.SandboxInfo`\n154: \n155: #### Scenario: 未知 sessionID 返回 SessionNotFoundError\n156: \n157: - **GIVEN** Store 中不存在 `sess-unknown` 条目\n158: - **WHEN** `GetSandboxBySession(ctx, \"sess-unknown\", ...)` 被调用\n159: - **THEN** 返回 `NewSessionNotFoundError(\"sess-unknown\")`\n160: \n161: #### Scenario: 空 sessionID 触发 WorkloadManager 创建\n162: \n163: - **GIVEN** `sessionID` 为空字符串，`WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` 已设置\n164: - **WHEN** `GetSandboxBySession(ctx, \"\", \"default\", \"my-runtime\", \"AgentRuntime\")` 被调用\n165: - **THEN** POST JSON `{\"kind\":\"AgentRuntime\",\"name\":\"my-runtime\",\"namespace\":\"default\"}` 到 `{WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL}/v1/agent-runtime`\n166: \n167: #### Scenario: WorkloadManager 非 200 返回模板未找到错误\n168: \n169: - **GIVEN** WorkloadManager 返回 HTTP 404\n170: - **WHEN** 空 sessionID 的创建请求被处理\n171: - **THEN** 返回 `NewSandboxTemplateNotFoundError(\"default\", \"my-runtime\", \"AgentRuntime\")`\n172: \n173: #### Scenario: 创建响应 sessionId 为空返回内部错误\n174: \n175: - **GIVEN** WorkloadManager 返回 HTTP 200，但响应体 `sessionId` 字段为空\n176: - **WHEN** 响应被解析\n177: - **THEN** 返回内部错误\n178: \n179: #### Scenario: In-cluster token 附加到创建请求\n180: \n181: - **GIVEN** `/var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/token` 存在且包含 `\"token-abc123\"`\n182: - **WHEN** 空 sessionID 的创建请求被发送\n183: - **THEN** 请求携带 `Authorization: Bearer token-abc123`\n184: \n185: #### Scenario: Service account token 文件不存在时不附加 Auth header\n186: \n187: - **GIVEN** `/var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/token` 不存在\n188: - **WHEN** 空 sessionID 的创建请求被发送\n189: - **THEN** 请求不携带 `Authorization` header，不 panic\n190: \n191: ---\n192: \n193: ### Requirement: JWTManager 与密钥管理\n194: \n195: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/jwt.go` 中定义 `JWTManager`：\n196: \n197: **常量：**\n198: \n199: | 名称 | 值 |\n200: |------|-----|\n201: | `rsaKeySize` | `2048` |\n202: | `jwtExpiration` | `5 * time.Minute` |\n203: | `IdentitySecretName` | `\"picod-router-identity\"` |\n204: | `PrivateKeyDataKey` | `\"private.pem\"` |\n205: | `PublicKeyDataKey` | `\"public.pem\"` |\n206: \n207: **变量：**\n208: - `IdentityNamespace` — 初始值 `\"default\"`，`init()` 中若 `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` 环境变量存在则覆盖\n209: \n210: ```go\n211: type JWTManager struct {\n212:     privateKey *rsa.PrivateKey\n213:     publicKey  *rsa.PublicKey\n214:     clientset  kubernetes.Interface\n215: }\n216: ```\n217: \n218: `NewJWTManager()` SHALL 生成 RSA 2048-bit 密钥对（`rsa.GenerateKey(rand.Reader, rsaKeySize)`）。\n219: \n220: `GenerateToken(claims map[string]interface{}) (string, error)` SHALL：\n221: 1. 设置基础 claims：`exp` = now + jwtExpiration（Unix 时间戳），`iat` = now（Unix 时间戳），`iss` = `\"agentcube-router\"`\n222: 2. 合并自定义 claims\n223: 3. 使用 `jwt.SigningMethodRS256` 签名，返回 JWT 字符串\n224: \n225: `TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret(ctx) error` SHALL：\n226: 1. 若 `clientset == nil`，尝试 `rest.InClusterConfig()`；失败则 log warning 并返回 nil（ephemeral keys 路径）\n227: 2. 构造 Secret：`IdentitySecretName`，namespace 为 `IdentityNamespace`，type `Opaque`，labels `app=agentcube` + `component=router`，data 包含 `private.pem`（PKCS1 PEM）和 `public.pem`（PKIX PEM）\n228: 3. 尝试 Create；若 `AlreadyExists`，Get Secret 并调用 `loadPrivateKeyPEM` 加载私钥\n229: \n230: #### Scenario: 新集群中创建 JWT Secret\n231: \n232: - **GIVEN** in-cluster config 成功，Secret `picod-router-identity` 不存在\n233: - **WHEN** `TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret(ctx)` 被调用\n234: - **THEN** 创建 opaque Secret，包含 `private.pem` 和 `public.pem`\n235: \n236: #### Scenario: 已存在 Secret 时加载私钥\n237: \n238: - **GIVEN** Secret `picod-router-identity` 已存在\n239: - **WHEN** `TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret(ctx)` 被调用\n240: - **THEN** 不创建新 Secret，从 Secret 中加载 `private.pem` 到 `privateKey`\n241: \n242: #### Scenario: 非 in-cluster 环境使用 ephemeral keys\n243: \n244: - **GIVEN** `clientset == nil` 且 `rest.InClusterConfig()` 失败\n245: - **WHEN** `TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret(ctx)` 被调用\n246: - **THEN** 发出 warning 日志，返回 nil，使用内存中的 ephemeral 密钥对\n247: \n248: #### Scenario: JWT token 包含标准 claims\n249: \n250: - **GIVEN** `JWTManager` 已初始化\n251: - **WHEN** `GenerateToken(map[string]interface{}{\"session_id\": \"sess-001\"})` 被调用\n252: - **THEN** 返回的 JWT 包含 `exp`（5 分钟后）、`iat`（当前时间）、`iss`（`\"agentcube-router\"`）和 `session_id`（`\"sess-001\"`）\n253: \n254: #### Scenario: JWT 使用 RS256 算法签名\n255: \n256: - **GIVEN** `JWTManager` 已初始化\n257: - **WHEN** `GenerateToken(...)` 被调用\n258: - **THEN** JWT header 中 `alg` 为 `\"RS256\"`\n259: \n260: #### Scenario: AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE 覆盖默认 namespace\n261: \n262: - **GIVEN** 环境变量 `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE = \"agentcube-prod\"`\n263: - **WHEN** 包初始化完成\n264: - **THEN** `IdentityNamespace = \"agentcube-prod\"`\n265: \n266: ---\n267: \n268: ### Requirement: 反向代理到 Sandbox\n269: \n270: The system SHALL 使用 `httputil.NewSingleHostReverseProxy(targetURL)` 构建反向代理，`proxy.Transport = s.httpTransport`。\n271: \n272: Upstream URL 确定逻辑：\n273: 1. 从 `SandboxInfo.EntryPoints` 中查找第一个 `path` 前缀匹配 invocation path 的 entry point\n274: 2. 若无匹配，使用第一个 entry point\n275: 3. 若 `EntryPoints` 为空，返回 404 JSON `{\"error\":\"no entry point found for sandbox\"}`\n276: \n277: URL 构建：若 `protocol` 已设置且 `endpoint` 不含 scheme，则在 `endpoint` 前拼接 `protocol`（小写）+ `\"://\"`。\n278: \n279: Director SHALL：\n280: 1. 设置 `req.URL.Path` 为规范化后的路径（Gin path param 若无前导 `/` 则添加）\n281: 2. 清除 `req.URL.RawPath`\n282: 3. 设置 `req.Host = targetURL.Host`\n283: 4. 设置转发 headers（见 Requirement: Forwarding headers）\n284: 5. 若 JWT 非空，设置 `Authorization: Bearer <token>`\n285: \n286: ModifyResponse SHALL 设置响应 header `x-agentcube-session-id` 为 resolved session ID。\n287: \n288: #### Scenario: EntryPoints 为空返回 404\n289: \n290: - **GIVEN** `SandboxInfo.EntryPoints` 为空切片\n291: - **WHEN** 反向代理处理请求\n292: - **THEN** 响应 404，body 为 JSON `{\"error\":\"no entry point found for sandbox\"}`\n293: \n294: #### Scenario: 匹配 path 前缀选择 entry point\n295: \n296: - **GIVEN** `EntryPoints` 包含两个 entry：`{path: \"/api\", endpoint: \"sandbox:8080\"}` 和 `{path: \"/ws\", endpoint: \"sandbox:8081\"}`\n297: - **AND** invocation path 为 `/api/users`\n298: - **WHEN** upstream 被确定\n299: - **THEN** 选择第一个 entry point（`/api` 匹配）\n300: \n301: #### Scenario: 无匹配时使用第一个 entry point\n302: \n303: - **GIVEN** `EntryPoints` 包含 `{path: \"/api\", endpoint: \"sandbox:8080\"}`\n304: - **AND** invocation path 为 `/other/path`\n305: - **WHEN** upstream 被确定\n306: - **THEN** 使用第一个 entry point\n307: \n308: #### Scenario: Endpoint 不含 scheme 时拼接 protocol\n309: \n310: - **GIVEN** entry point `protocol = \"http\"`，`endpoint = \"sandbox:8080\"`\n311: - **WHEN** upstream URL 被构建\n312: - **THEN** 目标 URL 为 `http://sandbox:8080`\n313: \n314: #### Scenario: Path 无前导斜杠时自动添加\n315: \n316: - **GIVEN** Gin path param `*path` 值为 `\"users/123\"`（无前导 `/`）\n317: - **WHEN** Director 运行\n318: - **THEN** `req.URL.Path` 被设为 `\"/users/123\"`\n319: \n320: #### Scenario: ModifyResponse 设置 session ID header\n321: \n322: - **GIVEN** session ID 为 `\"sess-001\"`\n323: - **WHEN** 代理响应返回\n324: - **THEN** 响应 header 包含 `x-agentcube-session-id: sess-001`\n325: \n326: ---\n327: \n328: ### Requirement: JWT 注入\n329: \n330: For sandbox kinds `Sandbox` 和 `SandboxClaim`，the system SHALL 在代理前生成 JWT 并设置 `Authorization: Bearer <token>` 到代理请求。\n331: \n332: #### Scenario: JWT 签名失败返回 500\n333: \n334: - **GIVEN** JWT 生成返回错误\n335: - **WHEN** 转发请求\n336: - **THEN** 响应 500，body 为 JSON 包含 `\"code\":\"JWT_SIGNING_FAILED\"` 和 `\"error\":\"failed to sign request\"`\n337: \n338: #### Scenario: 非 Sandbox/SandboxClaim kind 不注入 JWT\n339: \n340: - **GIVEN** sandbox kind 为 `PicoD`\n341: - **WHEN** 代理请求被构建\n342: - **THEN** 不设置 `Authorization` header\n343: \n344: ---\n345: \n346: ### Requirement: Forwarding headers 与响应 header\n347: \n348: The system SHALL 在 Director 中设置以下转发 headers：\n349: - `X-Forwarded-Host`：来自原始请求的 `Host`\n350: - `X-Forwarded-Proto`：TLS 存在时为 `\"https\"`，否则 `\"http\"`\n351: - `X-Forwarded-For`：将客户端 IP 追加到已有值（逗号分隔）\n352: \n353: The system SHALL 在 ModifyResponse 中设置响应 header `x-agentcube-session-id` 为 resolved session ID。\n354: \n355: #### Scenario: X-Forwarded-For 追加客户端 IP\n356: \n357: - **GIVEN** 原始请求已有 `X-Forwarded-For: 1.2.3.4`\n358: - **AND** 客户端 IP 为 `5.6.7.8`\n359: - **WHEN** Director 运行\n360: - **THEN** `X-Forwarded-For` 被设为 `\"1.2.3.4, 5.6.7.8\"`\n361: \n362: #### Scenario: X-Forwarded-Proto 为 http\n363: \n364: - **GIVEN** 请求未使用 TLS\n365: - **WHEN** Director 运行\n366: - **THEN** `X-Forwarded-Proto` 被设为 `\"http\"`\n367: \n368: ---\n369: \n370: ### Requirement: 代理错误映射\n371: \n372: The system SHALL 在 `ErrorHandler` 中映射代理错误：\n373: - 错误信息包含 `\"connection refused\"` → 502 `{\"error\":\"sandbox unreachable\"}`\n374: - 错误信息包含 `\"timeout\"` → 504 `{\"error\":\"sandbox timeout\"}`\n375: - 其他错误 → 502 `{\"error\":\"sandbox unreachable\"}`\n376: \n377: #### Scenario: 下游连接被拒绝\n378: \n379: - **GIVEN** 反向代理错误信息包含 `\"connection refused\"`\n380: - **WHEN** `ErrorHandler` 运行\n381: - **THEN** 响应 502，body 为 JSON `{\"error\":\"sandbox unreachable\"}`\n382: \n383: #### Scenario: 下游超时\n384: \n385: - **GIVEN** 反向代理错误信息包含 `\"timeout\"`\n386: - **WHEN** `ErrorHandler` 运行\n387: - **THEN** 响应 504，body 为 JSON `{\"error\":\"sandbox timeout\"}`\n388: \n389: #### Scenario: 其他代理错误\n390: \n391: - **GIVEN** 反向代理错误信息为 `\"dial tcp: lookup sandbox: no such host\"`\n392: - **WHEN** `ErrorHandler` 运行\n393: - **THEN** 响应 502，body 为 JSON `{\"error\":\"sandbox unreachable\"}`\n394: \n395: ---\n396: \n397: ### Requirement: Last-activity 更新\n398: \n399: The system SHALL 在成功解析 sandbox 后调用 `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, sessionID, time.Now())`，并在 `forwardToSandbox` 返回后再次调用（每次成功 invoke 路径调用两次）。失败 SHALL 仅记录 warning 日志，不阻断代理流程。\n400: \n401: #### Scenario: Store 更新失败不阻断代理\n402: \n403: - **GIVEN** `UpdateSessionLastActivity` 返回错误\n404: - **WHEN** sandbox 解析成功\n405: - **THEN** 代理仍然执行，错误仅被记录为 warning\n406: \n407: #### Scenario: 成功路径调用两次 UpdateSessionLastActivity\n408: \n409: - **GIVEN** sandbox 解析成功且代理转发成功\n410: - **WHEN** invoke handler 完成\n411: - **THEN** `UpdateSessionLastActivity` 被调用两次（解析后和转发后）\n412: \n413: ---\n414: \n415: ### Requirement: Health 端点\n416: \n417: The system SHALL 注册以下 health 端点：\n418: \n419: | Method | Path | Handler | 响应 |\n420: |--------|------|---------|------|\n421: | GET | `/health/live` | `handleHealthLive` | 200 `{\"status\":\"alive\"}` |\n422: | GET | `/health/ready` | `handleHealthReady` | 见下 |\n423: \n424: `handleHealthReady` SHALL：\n425: - 若 `sessionManager` 非 nil，返回 200 `{\"status\":\"ready\"}`\n426: - 若 `sessionManager` 为 nil，返回 503 `{\"status\":\"not ready\",\"error\":\"session manager not available\"}`\n427: \n428: Health 端点 SHALL 不经过任何中间件（无 logger、recovery、concurrency limit）。\n429: \n430: #### Scenario: Liveness 始终返回 200\n431: \n432: - **GIVEN** Server 已启动\n433: - **WHEN** `GET /health/live` 被请求\n434: - **THEN** 响应 200，body 为 JSON `{\"status\":\"alive\"}`\n435: \n436: #### Scenario: Readiness 依赖 sessionManager\n437: \n438: - **GIVEN** `sessionManager` 为 nil\n439: - **WHEN** `GET /health/ready` 被请求\n440: - **THEN** 响应 503，body 包含 `\"error\":\"session manager not available\"`\n441: \n442: #### Scenario: Readiness 返回 200 当 sessionManager 可用\n443: \n444: - **GIVEN** `sessionManager` 非 nil\n445: - **WHEN** `GET /health/ready` 被请求\n446: - **THEN** 响应 200，body 为 JSON `{\"status\":\"ready\"}`\n447: \n448: ---\n449: \n450: ### Requirement: 并发限制中间件\n451: \n452: The system SHALL 实现基于 buffered channel 的信号量中间件 `concurrencyLimitMiddleware`，容量为 `config.MaxConcurrentRequests`。\n453: \n454: 中间件行为：\n455: 1. 尝试向 channel 发送（非阻塞 `select` + `default`）\n456: 2. 若发送成功，执行 `c.Next()`，完成后从 channel 接收释放槽位\n457: 3. 若发送失败（无可用槽位），响应 429 JSON `{\"error\":\"server overloaded, please try again later\",\"code\":\"SERVER_OVERLOADED\"}` 并 `c.Abort()`\n458: \n459: 该中间件 SHALL 仅应用于 `/v1` 路由组，不应用于 health 端点。\n460: \n461: #### Scenario: 并发槽位可用时请求通过\n462: \n463: - **GIVEN** 当前并发数 < `MaxConcurrentRequests`\n464: - **WHEN** 请求到达 `/v1/...` 路由\n465: - **THEN** 请求被正常处理\n466: \n467: #### Scenario: 并发槽位耗尽时返回 429\n468: \n469: - **GIVEN** 当前并发数 = `MaxConcurrentRequests`\n470: - **WHEN** 新请求到达 `/v1/...` 路由\n471: - **THEN** 响应 429，body 为 JSON `{\"error\":\"server overloaded, please try again later\",\"code\":\"SERVER_OVERLOADED\"}`\n472: \n473: #### Scenario: 请求完成后释放槽位\n474: \n475: - **GIVEN** 一个请求占用了并发槽位\n476: - **WHEN** 请求处理完成\n477: - **THEN** 槽位被释放，可被后续请求使用\n478: \n479: #### Scenario: Health 端点不受并发限制\n480: \n481: - **GIVEN** 并发槽位已耗尽\n482: - **WHEN** `GET /health/live` 被请求\n483: - **THEN** 请求正常处理，返回 200\n484: \n485: ---\n486: \n487: ### Requirement: 调用路由注册\n488: \n489: The system SHALL 注册以下路由到 Gin engine：\n490: \n491: | Method | Path | Middleware | Handler |\n492: |--------|------|------------|---------|\n493: | GET | `/health/live` | none | `handleHealthLive` |\n494: | GET | `/health/ready` | none | `handleHealthReady` |\n495: | GET | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/invocations/*path` | `gin.Logger`, `gin.Recovery`, `concurrencyLimitMiddleware` | `handleAgentInvoke` |\n496: | POST | 同上 | 同上 | `handleAgentInvoke` |\n497: | GET | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/invocations/*path` | 同上 | `handleCodeInterpreterInvoke` |\n498: | POST | 同上 | 同上 | `handleCodeInterpreterInvoke` |\n499: \n500: `/v1` 路由组 SHALL 使用 `gin.Logger()`、`gin.Recovery()` 和 `concurrencyLimitMiddleware` 中间件。\n501: \n502: `handleAgentInvoke` SHALL 以 `types.AgentRuntimeKind` 作为 kind 参数调用 session lookup。\n503: `handleCodeInterpreterInvoke` SHALL 以 `types.CodeInterpreterKind` 作为 kind 参数调用 session lookup。\n504: \n505: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime 调用使用正确的 kind\n506: \n507: - **GIVEN** 请求 `GET /v1/namespaces/default/agent-runtimes/my-runtime/invocations/api/users`\n508: - **WHEN** `handleAgentInvoke` 运行\n509: - **THEN** kind 参数为 `types.AgentRuntimeKind`\n510: \n511: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter 调用使用正确的 kind\n512: \n513: - **GIVEN** 请求 `POST /v1/namespaces/default/code-interpreters/my-ci/invocations/execute`\n514: - **WHEN** `handleCodeInterpreterInvoke` 运行\n515: - **THEN** kind 参数为 `types.CodeInterpreterKind`\n516: \n517: #### Scenario: GET 和 POST 均支持\n518: \n519: - **GIVEN** 路由已注册\n520: - **WHEN** `GET /v1/namespaces/default/agent-runtimes/my-runtime/invocations/` 被请求\n521: - **THEN** `handleAgentInvoke` 被调用\n522: - **WHEN** `POST /v1/namespaces/default/agent-runtimes/my-runtime/invocations/` 被请求\n523: - **THEN** `handleAgentInvoke` 被调用\n524: \n525: ---\n526: \n527: ### Requirement: HTTP 服务器行为\n528: \n529: The system SHALL 配置 `http.Server`：\n530: - `ReadTimeout: 30 * time.Second`\n531: - `IdleTimeout: 90 * time.Second`\n532: - 使用 `h2c` 和 `http2.Server` 支持 HTTP/2 明文升级\n533: \n534: `Start()` 方法 SHALL：\n535: 1. 若 `config.EnableTLS = true` 且 `TLSCert` 或 `TLSKey` 为空，返回错误 `\"TLS cert and key must both be provided\"`\n536: 2. 若 TLS 启用，调用 `httpServer.ListenAndServeTLS(config.TLSCert, config.TLSKey)`\n537: 3. 否则调用支持 h2c 的启动方式\n538: \n539: `Stop(ctx)` 方法 SHALL：\n540: 1. 在 context 取消时调用 `httpServer.Shutdown(ctx)`\n541: 2. Shutdown 超时 10 秒\n542: \n543: #### Scenario: TLS 配置不完整返回错误\n544: \n545: - **GIVEN** `config.EnableTLS = true` 且 `config.TLSCert = \"\"`\n546: - **WHEN** `Start()` 被调用\n547: - **THEN** 返回错误 `\"TLS cert and key must both be provided\"`\n548: \n549: #### Scenario: 正常启动无 TLS\n550: \n551: - **GIVEN** `config.EnableTLS = false`\n552: - **WHEN** `Start()` 被调用\n553: - **THEN** 服务器在 `config.Port` 上监听，支持 h2c\n554: \n555: #### Scenario: 优雅关闭在 10 秒内完成\n556: \n557: - **GIVEN** 服务器正在运行，有活跃连接\n558: - **WHEN** context 被取消\n559: - **THEN** `httpServer.Shutdown` 在 10 秒超时内完成\n560: \n561: ---\n562: \n563: ### Requirement: CRD Informer 集成\n564: \n565: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/informer.go` 中使用 `client-go` 的 Informer 机制监听 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 变更：\n566: \n567: 1. 使用 `SharedInformerFactory`（`informers.NewSharedInformerFactory(clientset, 30*time.Second)`）\n568: 2. 获取 `agentRuntimeInformer = factory.Runtime().V1alpha1().AgentRuntimes()`\n569: 3. 获取 `codeInterpreterInformer = factory.Runtime().V1alpha1().CodeInterpreters()`\n570: 4. 注册事件处理器：\n571: \n572: ```go\n573: agentRuntimeInformer.Informer().AddEventHandler(cache.ResourceEventHandlerFuncs{\n574:     AddFunc:    onAgentRuntimeAdded,\n575:     UpdateFunc: onAgentRuntimeUpdated,\n576:     DeleteFunc: onAgentRuntimeDeleted,\n577: })\n578: ```\n579: \n580: 5. 使用 `Lister` 接口进行本地缓存查询，减少 API Server 压力\n581: 6. Informer 启动后调用 `factory.Start(stopCh)` 和 `factory.WaitForCacheSync(stopCh)`\n582: \n583: 事件处理器 SHALL 更新内部路由表（`AddRoute`/`RemoveRoute`）。\n584: \n585: #### Scenario: Informer 监听 AgentRuntime 新增\n586: \n587: - **GIVEN** Informer 已启动并同步\n588: - **WHEN** 新的 AgentRuntime CR 被创建\n589: - **THEN** `onAgentRuntimeAdded` 被调用，路由表被更新\n590: \n591: #### Scenario: Informer 监听 CodeInterpreter 更新\n592: \n593: - **GIVEN** Informer 已启动并同步\n594: - **WHEN** CodeInterpreter CR 被更新\n595: - **THEN** `onCodeInterpreterUpdated` 被调用，路由表被更新\n596: \n597: #### Scenario: Informer 监听 CR 删除\n598: \n599: - **GIVEN** Informer 已启动并同步\n600: - **WHEN** AgentRuntime CR 被删除\n601: - **THEN** `onAgentRuntimeDeleted` 被调用，对应路由从路由表移除\n602: \n603: #### Scenario: Lister 查询不经过 API Server\n604: \n605: - **GIVEN** Informer 缓存已同步\n606: - **WHEN** 通过 Lister 查询 AgentRuntime 列表\n607: - **THEN** 请求命中本地缓存，不产生 K8s API 调用\n608: \n609: ---\n610: \n611: ### Requirement: 路由管理（AddRoute/RemoveRoute）\n612: \n613: The system SHALL 实现 `Router` 接口：\n614: \n615: ```go\n616: type Router interface {\n617:     AddRoute(pattern string, backend Backend) error\n618:     RemoveRoute(pattern string) error\n619:     ServeHTTP(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request)\n620: }\n621: \n622: type Backend struct {\n623:     URL      *url.URL\n624:     Weight   int\n625:     Healthy  bool\n626: }\n627: ```\n628: \n629: `AddRoute` SHALL：\n630: 1. 验证 `pattern` 非空\n631: 2. 若 pattern 已存在，返回错误（或更新，见 tradeoff）\n632: 3. 将 pattern → Backend 映射存入路由表\n633: 4. 线程安全（使用 `sync.RWMutex` 保护）\n634: \n635: `RemoveRoute` SHALL：\n636: 1. 从路由表中移除 pattern\n637: 2. 若 pattern 不存在，返回 nil（幂等）\n638: 3. 线程安全\n639: \n640: `ServeHTTP` SHALL：\n641: 1. 根据请求路径匹配路由\n642: 2. 选择健康的 backend（负载均衡策略）\n643: 3. 若无匹配路由，返回 404\n644: 4. 代理请求到选中的 backend\n645: \n646: #### Scenario: 添加新路由\n647: \n648: - **GIVEN** 路由表为空\n649: - **WHEN** `AddRoute(\"/api/v1\", Backend{URL: &url.URL{Host: \"backend:8080\"}})` 被调用\n650: - **THEN** 路由表中存在该映射\n651: \n652: #### Scenario: 重复添加同一路由返回错误\n653: \n654: - **GIVEN** 路由表中已存在 pattern `\"/api/v1\"`\n655: - **WHEN** `AddRoute(\"/api/v1\", ...)` 再次被调用\n656: - **THEN** 返回错误\n657: \n658: #### Scenario: 移除不存在的路由幂等返回 nil\n659: \n660: - **GIVEN** 路由表中不存在 pattern `\"/api/v2\"`\n661: - **WHEN** `RemoveRoute(\"/api/v2\")` 被调用\n662: - **THEN** 返回 nil，无错误\n663: \n664: #### Scenario: 并发添加删路由不产生 data race\n665: \n666: - **GIVEN** 多个 goroutine 同时调用 `AddRoute` 和 `RemoveRoute`\n667: - **WHEN** 操作执行\n668: - **THEN** 无 data race，路由表状态一致\n669: \n670: #### Scenario: 无匹配路由返回 404\n671: \n672: - **GIVEN** 请求路径 `/unknown/path`\n673: - **AND** 路由表中无匹配项\n674: - **WHEN** `ServeHTTP` 被调用\n675: - **THEN** 响应 404\n676: \n677: ---\n678: \n679: ### Requirement: 负载均衡策略\n680: \n681: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/loadbalancer.go` 中实现以下负载均衡策略：\n682: \n683: **Round-Robin：**\n684: - 按顺序循环选择 backend\n685: - 跳过不健康的 backend\n686: - 线程安全的计数器\n687: \n688: **Least-Connections：**\n689: - 选择当前活跃连接数最少的健康 backend\n690: - 使用原子计数器跟踪连接数\n691: \n692: 策略选择 SHALL 可通过配置指定，默认 Round-Robin。\n693: \n694: #### Scenario: Round-Robin 循环选择\n695: \n696: - **GIVEN** 三个健康 backend：A、B、C\n697: - **WHEN** 连续三次选择\n698: - **THEN** 依次选择 A、B、C\n699: \n700: #### Scenario: Round-Robin 跳过不健康 backend\n701: \n702: - **GIVEN** 三个 backend：A（健康）、B（不健康）、C（健康）\n703: - **WHEN** Round-Robin 选择\n704: - **THEN** 只选择 A 和 C，跳过 B\n705: \n706: #### Scenario: 所有 backend 不健康\n707: \n708: - **GIVEN** 所有 backend 的 `Healthy = false`\n709: - **WHEN** 负载均衡选择 backend\n710: - **THEN** 返回错误 `\"no healthy backend available\"`\n711: \n712: #### Scenario: Least-Connections 选择连接数最少的\n713: \n714: - **GIVEN** Backend A 有 5 个活跃连接，Backend B 有 2 个\n715: - **WHEN** Least-Connections 策略选择\n716: - **THEN** 选择 Backend B\n717: \n718: ---\n719: \n720: ### Requirement: Backend 健康检查\n721: \n722: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/backend.go` 中实现 backend 健康检查：\n723: \n724: 1. 定期对每个 backend 的 `URL` 发送 HTTP GET 请求（默认 `/health` 路径，30 秒间隔）\n725: 2. 响应 2xx 标记为 `Healthy = true`\n726: 3. 响应非 2xx 或超时标记为 `Healthy = false`\n727: 4. 连续失败 N 次（默认 3 次）后才标记为不健康（避免抖动）\n728: 5. 连续成功 M 次（默认 2 次）后才标记为健康（避免抖动）\n729: \n730: #### Scenario: 健康检查成功标记为健康\n731: \n732: - **GIVEN** backend 连续 2 次健康检查返回 200\n733: - **WHEN** 健康状态被评估\n734: - **THEN** `Healthy = true`\n735: \n736: #### Scenario: 健康检查连续失败标记为不健康\n737: \n738: - **GIVEN** backend 连续 3 次健康检查返回 500\n739: - **WHEN** 健康状态被评估\n740: - **THEN** `Healthy = false`\n741: \n742: #### Scenario: 单次失败不立即标记为不健康\n743: \n744: - **GIVEN** backend 之前健康，本次健康检查返回 500\n745: - **AND** 连续失败次数为 1（阈值 3）\n746: - **WHEN** 健康状态被评估\n747: - **THEN** `Healthy` 保持 `true`\n748: \n749: ---\n750: \n751: ### Requirement: 中间件（日志、追踪、限流）\n752: \n753: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/middleware.go` 中实现以下中间件：\n754: \n755: **请求日志中间件：**\n756: - 记录请求方法、路径、响应状态码、耗时\n757: - 使用结构化日志（`slog`）\n758: \n759: **Trace ID 注入中间件：**\n760: - 生成唯一 Trace ID（UUID v4）\n761: - 设置请求 header `X-Trace-Id`\n762: - 设置响应 header `X-Trace-Id`\n763: \n764: **基础限流中间件（可选）：**\n765: - 基于令牌桶算法\n766: - 默认速率：100 req/s，桶容量 200\n767: - 超限返回 429\n768: \n769: #### Scenario: Trace ID 注入请求和响应\n770: \n771: - **GIVEN** 请求到达\n772: - **WHEN** Trace ID 中间件运行\n773: - **THEN** 请求 header 包含 `X-Trace-Id: <uuid>`\n774: - **AND** 响应 header 包含 `X-Trace-Id: <uuid>`（相同值）\n775: \n776: #### Scenario: 请求日志包含方法和耗时\n777: \n778: - **GIVEN** 请求 `GET /v1/...` 耗时 150ms\n779: - **WHEN** 请求完成\n780: - **THEN** 日志包含 `method=GET`，`path=/v1/...`，`status=200`，`duration_ms=150`\n781: \n782: ---\n783: \n784: ### Requirement: 编译与测试门禁\n785: \n786: The system SHALL 满足以下门禁：\n787: 1. `go build ./pkg/router/...` 编译通过\n788: 2. `go build ./cmd/router/...` 编译通过\n789: 3. `go test ./pkg/router/... -v` 全部通过\n790: 4. `go test -race ./pkg/router/...` 无 data race 告警\n791: 5. 无 `log.Printf` 残留（使用 `slog` 或 `klog`）\n792: \n793: #### Scenario: pkg/router 编译通过\n794: \n795: - **GIVEN** 所有 router 代码已编写完成\n796: - **WHEN** `go build ./pkg/router/...` 执行\n797: - **THEN** 无编译错误\n798: \n799: #### Scenario: cmd/router 编译通过\n800: \n801: - **GIVEN** 所有 router 代码已编写完成\n802: - **WHEN** `go build ./cmd/router/...` 执行\n803: - **THEN** 无编译错误\n804: \n805: #### Scenario: 所有单元测试通过\n806: \n807: - **GIVEN** 测试用例已编写\n808: - **WHEN** `go test ./pkg/router/... -v` 执行\n809: - **THEN** 所有测试通过\n810: \n811: #### Scenario: Race detector 无告警\n812: \n813: - **GIVEN** 并发场景测试已覆盖（路由表、负载均衡、健康检查）\n814: - **WHEN** `go test -race ./pkg/router/...` 执行\n815: - **THEN** 无 data race 告警\n816: \n817: #### Scenario: 无 log.Printf 残留\n818: \n819: - **GIVEN** 所有日志已使用 `slog` 或 `klog`\n820: - **WHEN** `grep -rn 'log\\.Printf' pkg/router/` 执行\n821: - **THEN** 无匹配结果\n\n(End of file - total 821 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-009: Router HTTP 反向代理核心 — Delta Spec\n\n## Purpose\n\n为 agentcube 项目新建 `pkg/router` 模块，实现基于 Go 的 HTTP 反向代理核心，作为系统的流量入口。该模块负责：(1) 通过 session ID 解析或创建 sandbox，(2) 将 HTTP 请求反向代理到 sandbox pod 的 entry point，(3) 为 sandbox 请求注入 RS256 JWT 签名，(4) 通过 client-go Informer 监听 CRD 变更实现动态服务发现，(5) 提供负载均衡、健康检查、并发限制中间件。本变更是对 AR-003（CRD 类型定义）、AR-005（Sandbox 创建）、AR-007（Reconciler）的下游消费方，同时解锁 AR-010+ 的高级流量治理能力。\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: Config 结构体与 CLI 标志\n\nThe system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/config.go` 中定义 `Config` 结构体，包含以下字段：\n- `Port string` — 监听端口，默认 `\"8080\"`\n- `Debug bool` — 是否启用 Gin debug 模式，默认 `false`\n- `EnableTLS bool` — 是否启用 TLS，默认 `false`\n- `TLSCert string` — TLS 证书路径\n- `TLSKey string` — TLS 私钥路径\n- `MaxConcurrentRequests int` — 最大并发请求数，默认 `1000`（≤0 时 NewServer 内部设为 1000）\n\n`cmd/router/main.go` SHALL 解析以下 CLI 标志并构造 `Config`：\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775832708347,"end":1775832708355}}}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1775832708439,"sessionID":"ses_2882059dfffe6muPqJaYrql7KT","part":{"id":"prt_d77e0b53e001RujpObCF4M71nV","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","messageID":"msg_d77e0aa49001ISIc1QXznrBNnx","sessionID":"ses_2882059dfffe6muPqJaYrql7KT","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":27899,"input":27812,"output":72,"reasoning":15,"cache":{"write":0,"read":0}},"cost":0.007819749}}
{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775832712229,"sessionID":"ses_2882059dfffe6muPqJaYrql7KT","part":{"id":"prt_d77e0c41e0010RAVUdP1Uz4hD8","messageID":"msg_d77e0b56e0014D1vJN8oWyCViV","sessionID":"ses_2882059dfffe6muPqJaYrql7KT","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"text","timestamp":1775832765189,"sessionID":"ses_2882059dfffe6muPqJaYrql7KT","part":{"id":"prt_d77e0d14b001twZQuw5QILqIBs","messageID":"msg_d77e0b56e0014D1vJN8oWyCViV","sessionID":"ses_2882059dfffe6muPqJaYrql7KT","type":"text","text":"Now I'll write the delta-spec.md for AR-012:","time":{"start":1775832765187,"end":1775832765187}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775832765241,"sessionID":"ses_2882059dfffe6muPqJaYrql7KT","part":{"id":"prt_d77e0d236001DORxGVlVYqky69","messageID":"msg_d77e0b56e0014D1vJN8oWyCViV","sessionID":"ses_2882059dfffe6muPqJaYrql7KT","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_e6325d1422d0465aa096701d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-012: 会话存储接口定义 — Delta Spec\n\n## Context\n\n- **Module:** `pkg/store`\n- **Language:** Go\n- **Size:** S\n- **Base specs:** `session-store/spec.md`, `session-store/design.md`, `deployment/client-go.md`\n\n## Delta Requirements\n\n### Requirement: Redis StoreSandbox pipeline commands\nThe Redis implementation SHALL execute `StoreSandbox` as a pipeline of three commands: `SETNX` on the session key with JSON value, `ZADD` on `session:expiry` with score = `ExpiresAt.Unix()`, and `ZADD` on `session:last_activity` with score = `time.Now().Unix()`. The system SHALL fail if any command in the pipeline returns an error.\n\n#### Scenario: Successful store pipeline\n- **GIVEN** a valid `SandboxInfo` with non-zero `ExpiresAt` and session id `s1`\n- **WHEN** `StoreSandbox(ctx, sandbox)` is called on the Redis store\n- **THEN** the pipeline executes `SETNX session:s1 <json>`, `ZADD session:expiry <expires_unix> s1`, `ZADD session:last_activity <now_unix> s1` and returns nil\n\n#### Scenario: Pipeline error propagation\n- **GIVEN** the Redis server is unreachable during `StoreSandbox`\n- **WHEN** the pipeline executes\n- **THEN** the method returns a non-nil error and no partial state is committed\n\n### Requirement: Redis UpdateSandbox XX semantics\nThe Redis implementation SHALL use `SET key value XX` for `UpdateSandbox`. If the key does not exist, the system SHALL return an error indicating the key does not exist.\n\n#### Scenario: Update existing key\n- **GIVEN** session key `session:s1` exists\n- **WHEN** `UpdateSandbox(ctx, sandbox)` is called\n- **THEN** the JSON value is overwritten and the method returns nil\n\n#### Scenario: Update missing key\n- **GIVEN** session key `session:s1` does not exist\n- **WHEN** `UpdateSandbox(ctx, sandbox)` is called\n- **THEN** the method returns an error containing `key not exists`\n\n### Requirement: Redis DeleteSandboxBySessionID pipeline\nThe Redis implementation SHALL execute `DeleteSandboxBySessionID` as a pipeline of three commands: `DEL` on the session key, `ZREM` on `session:expiry`, and `ZREM` on `session:last_activity`.\n\n#### Scenario: Full deletion\n- **GIVEN** session `s1` exists with entries in both ZSETs\n- **WHEN** `DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, \"s1\")` succeeds\n- **THEN** `GET session:s1` returns nil and both ZSETs no longer contain member `s1`\n\n### Requirement: Redis ListExpiredSandboxes query\nThe Redis implementation SHALL query `session:expiry` using `ZRANGEBYSCORE` with range `-inf` to `before.Unix()` and `LIMIT 0 limit`. When `limit <= 0`, the method SHALL return `nil, nil`.\n\n#### Scenario: List with limit zero\n- **GIVEN** expired sessions exist in the index\n- **WHEN** `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, before, 0)` is called\n- **THEN** the method returns `nil, nil` without querying Redis\n\n#### Scenario: List with positive limit\n- **GIVEN** three sessions have expiry scores ≤ `before.Unix()`\n- **WHEN** `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, before, 2)` is called\n- **THEN** at most two `SandboxInfo` pointers are returned\n\n### Requirement: Redis ListInactiveSandboxes query\nThe Redis implementation SHALL query `session:last_activity` using `ZRANGEBYSCORE` with range `-inf` to `before.Unix()` and `LIMIT 0 limit`. When `limit <= 0`, the method SHALL return `nil, nil`.\n\n#### Scenario: Inactive list with negative limit\n- **GIVEN** inactive sessions exist\n- **WHEN** `ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx, before, -1)` is called\n- **THEN** the method returns `nil, nil`\n\n### Requirement: Redis UpdateSessionLastActivity precondition\nThe Redis implementation SHALL verify the session key exists via `GET` before executing `ZADD` on `session:last_activity`. If the key is absent, the method SHALL return `ErrNotFound`. If `at` is zero time, the system SHALL use `time.Now()`.\n\n#### Scenario: Activity update with zero time\n- **GIVEN** session `s1` exists and `at` is `time.Time{}`\n- **WHEN** `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, \"s1\", at)` is called\n- **THEN** `ZADD session:last_activity <now_unix> s1` is executed\n\n#### Scenario: Activity update for missing session\n- **GIVEN** session `s1` does not exist\n- **WHEN** `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, \"s1\", now)` is called\n- **THEN** the method returns `ErrNotFound`\n\n### Requirement: Valkey StoreSandbox multi-command\nThe Valkey implementation SHALL execute `StoreSandbox` via `DoMulti` with `SETNX`, `ZADD` on `session:expiry`, and `ZADD` on `session:last_activity`.\n\n#### Scenario: Valkey store success\n- **GIVEN** a valid `SandboxInfo` with session id `v1`\n- **WHEN** `StoreSandbox(ctx, sandbox)` is called on the Valkey store\n- **THEN** `DoMulti` executes the three commands and returns nil\n\n### Requirement: Valkey UpdateSandbox response validation\nThe Valkey implementation SHALL use `SET ... XX` and validate the response string equals `OK`. If the response is not `OK`, the system SHALL return an error indicating the key does not exist.\n\n#### Scenario: Valkey update missing key\n- **GIVEN** session key `session:v1` does not exist\n- **WHEN** `UpdateSandbox(ctx, sandbox)` is called\n- **THEN** the response is not `OK` and an error is returned\n\n### Requirement: Valkey DeleteSandboxBySessionID multi-command\nThe Valkey implementation SHALL execute `DeleteSandboxBySessionID` via `DoMulti` with `DEL`, `ZREM` on `session:expiry`, and `ZREM` on `session:last_activity`.\n\n#### Scenario: Valkey full deletion\n- **GIVEN** session `v1` exists in both ZSETs\n- **WHEN** `DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, \"v1\")` succeeds\n- **THEN** all three commands complete and the session is fully removed\n\n### Requirement: Valkey ListExpiredSandboxes via Zrangebyscore\nThe Valkey implementation SHALL use `Zrangebyscore` with `Min(\"-inf\")`, `Max(before.Unix() as string)`, and `Limit(0, limit)`. When `limit <= 0`, the method SHALL return `nil, nil`.\n\n#### Scenario: Valkey expired list\n- **GIVEN** two sessions have expiry ≤ `before.Unix()`\n- **WHEN** `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, before, 5)` is called\n- **THEN** the method returns up to two `SandboxInfo` pointers\n\n### Requirement: Valkey UpdateSessionLastActivity Exists check\nThe Valkey implementation SHALL check key existence via `Exists` returning int64 ≥ 1 before `ZADD`. If `Exists` returns 0, the method SHALL return `ErrNotFound`. If `at` is zero time, the system SHALL use `time.Now()`.\n\n#### Scenario: Valkey activity bump missing session\n- **GIVEN** no key `session:v1`\n- **WHEN** `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, \"v1\", now)` is called\n- **THEN** `Exists` returns 0 and the method returns `ErrNotFound`\n\n### Requirement: Valkey MGET orphan tolerance\nThe Valkey implementation SHALL use `Mget` to load sandboxes by session IDs. Entries returning empty string SHALL be skipped without failing the batch.\n\n#### Scenario: Valkey orphan ZSET member\n- **GIVEN** session id `orphan` exists in `session:expiry` ZSET but `session:orphan` key is absent\n- **WHEN** `ListExpiredSandboxes` loads the batch\n- **THEN** `orphan` is omitted from the returned slice and no error is raised\n\n### Requirement: Redis pipeline GET orphan tolerance\nThe Redis implementation SHALL handle nil results from pipeline `GET` commands when loading sandboxes by session IDs. Entries with nil results SHALL be skipped without failing the batch.\n\n#### Scenario: Redis orphan ZSET member\n- **GIVEN** session id `ghost` is in `session:last_activity` but `session:ghost` does not exist\n- **WHEN** `ListInactiveSandboxes` loads the batch via pipeline GETs\n- **THEN** `ghost` is omitted from the result slice\n\n### Requirement: Redis password policy\nThe Redis implementation SHALL require non-empty `REDIS_PASSWORD` unless `REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED` is set case-insensitively to `false`.\n\n#### Scenario: Password required by default\n- **GIVEN** `REDIS_ADDR` is set, `REDIS_PASSWORD` is empty, and `REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED` is unset\n- **WHEN** the Redis store initializes\n- **THEN** initialization fails with an error stating password is required\n\n#### Scenario: Password not required\n- **GIVEN** `REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED=false` and `REDIS_PASSWORD` is empty\n- **WHEN** the Redis store initializes\n- **THEN** initialization proceeds without password error\n\n### Requirement: Valkey optional client flags\nThe Valkey implementation SHALL set `DisableCache` true when `VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE` parses as true via `strconv.ParseBool`. The system SHALL set `ForceSingleClient` true when `VALKEY_FORCE_SINGLE` parses as true.\n\n#### Scenario: Disable cache enabled\n- **GIVEN** `VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE=true`\n- **WHEN** Valkey client options are built\n- **THEN** `ClientOption.DisableCache` is true\n\n#### Scenario: Force single client enabled\n- **GIVEN** `VALKEY_FORCE_SINGLE=true`\n- **WHEN** Valkey client options are built\n- **THEN** `ClientOption.ForceSingleClient` is true\n\n### Requirement: Singleton initialization\nThe system SHALL use `sync.Once` to ensure `initStore` executes exactly once. `Storage()` SHALL call `initStoreOnce.Do(initStore)` and on error SHALL call `klog.Fatalf(\"init store failed: %v\", err)`.\n\n#### Scenario: Concurrent Storage calls\n- **GIVEN** ten goroutines call `Storage()` simultaneously\n- **WHEN** all calls complete\n- **THEN** `initStore` has executed exactly once and all goroutines receive the same `Store` instance\n\n### Requirement: Provider selection default\nWhen `STORE_TYPE` is unset or empty, the system SHALL default to `redis` (case-insensitive comparison).\n\n#### Scenario: Unset STORE_TYPE\n- **GIVEN** `STORE_TYPE` environment variable is not set\n- **WHEN** `Storage()` initializes\n- **THEN** the Redis implementation is constructed\n\n#### Scenario: Invalid STORE_TYPE\n- **GIVEN** `STORE_TYPE=memcached`\n- **WHEN** `Storage()` initializes\n- **THEN** initialization fails with an unsupported store type error\n\n### Requirement: Redis Ping response validation\nThe Redis implementation SHALL issue `PING` and validate the response equals `PONG`.\n\n#### Scenario: Healthy Redis\n- **GIVEN** Redis server is running\n- **WHEN** `Ping(ctx)` is called\n- **THEN** the response is `PONG` and nil error is returned\n\n### Requirement: Valkey Ping response validation\nThe Valkey implementation SHALL issue `B().Ping()` and validate the string response equals `PONG`.\n\n#### Scenario: Healthy Valkey\n- **GIVEN** Valkey server is running\n- **WHEN** `Ping(ctx)` is called\n- **THEN** the response string is `PONG` and nil error is returned\n\n### Requirement: StoreSandbox nil/zero validation\nThe system SHALL return an error when `StoreSandbox` is called with a nil `SandboxInfo` or when `ExpiresAt` is zero time.\n\n#### Scenario: Nil sandbox\n- **GIVEN** `StoreSandbox(ctx, nil)` is called\n- **WHEN** the method executes\n- **THEN** an error is returned indicating sandbox is nil\n\n#### Scenario: Zero ExpiresAt\n- **GIVEN** `SandboxInfo` has `ExpiresAt == time.Time{}`\n- **WHEN** `StoreSandbox(ctx, sandbox)` is called\n- **THEN** an error is returned indicating ExpiresAt is required\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775832765181,"end":1775832765238}}}}
